3 attempts to find RM1 Back Squat

EMOM for 6min:

For quality:
5 Strict Ring Muscle-ups
Rest 2min
4 Strict Ring Muscle-ups
Rest 1.5min

C.
"The Seven"
Seven rounds for time of:
7 Handstand push-ups
7 Thrusters (#60/40)
7 Knees to elbows
7 Deadlifts (#111/80)
7 Burpees
7 Kettlebell swings (#32/24)
